### Add new rule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/firewall/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "srcStart": "20.20.20.20",
  "srcEnd": "25.25.25.25",
  "destStart": "30.30.30.30",
  "destEnd": "35.35.35.35",
  "action": "ALLOW"
}

### Get firewall decision
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/firewall/decision?srcIp=21.21.21.21&destIp=32.32.32.32

###
